{
  "stem": "4919.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just former soldiers who escaped prison.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- and at the same village, I knew there was two more Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two more.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't communicate with each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't talk to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I knew about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I want to tell you a last episode, that was when I came to join the army, we got to go to a city of Valuyki.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's in Russia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's not Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's in Russia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they took us all to a school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from that school, they gave us the directions where I have to go to the city of Khar'kov.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The other guys have to go to another city to join the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We [? share ?] our battle there on the front.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we-- we got to sleep at the school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the second day, they call-- they called us all to the KGB.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the KGB-- headquarter of the KGB.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they got to check us, you know, because we have been at the occupation zone of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who are we?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I anticipate bad things, because I knew, if you are Jewish, they always said you couldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You should be killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if you survived, so you collaborated with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You got to be tried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You've got to go to jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, it was a row in the corridor of the school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a row, maybe 50 people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to the very end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It passed a few minutes, and I saw a Jewish guy went out from the room, by two people, by two convoys.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was arrested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, when I got in, I didn't say my real name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said just, I am Ivan [?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
